Package: LTNLDA
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of a collapsed blocked Gibbs Sampler for the LTN-LDA model
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-08-24
Author: Patrick LeBlanc
Maintainer: Patrick LeBlanc <patrick.m.leblanc@gmail.com>
Description: A package implementing the LTN-LDA model proposed in PAPER.  There are two 
    main functions in the package: LTNLDA and LTNLDA_Perplexity.  LTNLDA runs a collapsed 
    blocked Gibbs sampler for the LTN-LDA model.  LTNLDA_Perplexity estimates the perplexity
    of a fitted LTN-LDA model on a test set.  
LazyData: true
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.7), pgdraw, phyloseq, stats, MCMCpack, BayesianGLasso, BDgraph
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
